lead_paragraph:
PRINTZ-- Irene,

passed away peacefully on January 22, 2016 at age 89. Adoring wife of the late Norman, loving mother of Stephen, Michael and the late Elizabeth, grandmother of Jordan, Eryenne, Jaclyn, David and Aimee, and great-grandmother of Noah. Educated, refined and cultured, she raised a beautiful family, worked in the retail industry and was a collector of art. She was loved deeply and will be missed greatly. www.goldsteinsfuneral.com
